PMID== 10603420
TI  == isolation of bacteroides fragilis mutants with in vivo growth defects by using tn4400', a modified tn4400 transposition system, and a new screening method.
AB  == a modified version of the bacteroides fragilis transposon tn4400, designated tn4400', enabling rapid isolation and analysis of b. fragilis mutants has been constructed. to identify potential virulence factors, tn4400'-generated mutants were screened by a new method; this resulted in the isolation of 21 mutant strains with impaired growth characteristics on tissue culture monolayers but normal growth in rich medium anaerobically.
