PMID== 6990863
TI  == semielectronic turbidimeter for automated monitoring of bacterial growth in test  tubes.
AB  == an automated turbidimeter for measuring bacterial growth in ordinary test tubes is described. the device records and prints adsorbance, expressed as klett units, of 60 cultures every 15 min. provision is made for either aerobic or anaerobic incubation. the device is adaptable to modification, depending upon local requirements and availability of computation facilities.
