PMID== 6987938
TI  == wound infection: a controlled clinical and experimental demonstration of synergy  between aerobic (escherichia coli) and anaerobic (bacteroides fragilis) bacteria.
AB  == pathogenic synergy between escherichia coli and bacteroides fragilis was suggested by clinical trials and proved to exist in an experimental guinea-pig wound model. this finding is thought to have important theoretical and practical  therapeutic implications.
