PMID== 333042
TI  == transfer of multiple antibiotic resistance from bacteroides fragilis to escherichia coli.
AB  == multiple antibiotic resistance was transferred from a clinical isolate of bacteroides fragilis to a strain of escherichia coli k12. resistance to ampicillin, amoxicillin, cephalothin, tetracycline, minocycline, and chloramphenicol was transferred as a unit, but the resistance markers became segregated during storage of the recipient strains.
